data.description: Seller offering $10,000 concessions towards interest rate buydown and/or closing costs! Prime Bella Vista location near top attractions: Little Sugar mountain biking, Lake Windsor water fun, golf, and Tanyard Creek Walking trail. This airy home, embraced by lush greenery and natural privacy, will captivate you. The main level of this iconic midcentury Bella Vista floorplan boasts 2 bedrooms, a bonus room, large pantry, and 2 storage rooms. Downstairs offers versatile finished space: in-law suite, workshop, or game room. Your dream lifestyle begins here!
